high_descs: Turn 90 degrees to the left and walk, turning another 90 degrees to the right and walking towards the counter when you reach it.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn to the left 90 degrees and take a few steps, turning back to the right 90 degrees to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Walk slightly to the right back to the potato slice.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn to the left 270 degrees and walk for a little bit, turning to the left 90 degrees to face the stove when you reach it.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside, close it, wait a little bit, open the microwave, remove the potato, and close it.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk to the other end of the room, turning to he right 90 degrees when you reach table and walk towards it.
Place the potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, then turn right to approach the counter adjacent to the oven.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Move to the left and look back down at the counter.
Put the butter knife on the counter, to the left of the potato.
Move to the right to look at a potato.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Go to the oven to your right, and look up at the microwave.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave.
Turn around, go towards the door, then turn right, go straight, then turn right to face the table.
Put the potato slice on the table, in front of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato slice on the table.

high_descs: Step to the left and face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter.
Look up to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Look down to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the potato on the counter.
Take a step to the right and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, turn right and walk across the room and turn to the right to face the end of the table.
Place the potato slice on the end of the table.
anns.task_desc: Head a slice of potato and place it on the end of the table.

high_descs: Turn left and move over to the counter just left of the stove
Pick up the butter knife from the counter
Use the knife to slice the potato on the same counter
Move slightly left to face the same counter
Set the knife down on the counter just left of the potato
Move slightly right toward the stove to face the same counter
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter
Turn right and walk to the microwave above the stove
Put the potato in the microwave and cook it, then take it out
Turn around and carry the potato across the room to the white table
Set the potato down on the table to the right of the lettuce
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked potato on the white table

high_descs: Turn left, then right.  Stop at counter with vegetables and knife by the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter with the knife.
Twist to the left while holding knife and turn back to the counter.
Place knife on its end next to the sliced potato.
Twist to the right and then back to the counter.
Place the knife on the left side of the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.  Turn around completely, move slightly right until you are in front of the stove.
Place potato in the smaller pot on the back of the stove and brown it.
Pick up cooked potato and turn left.  Move across room to the dining table on your left.
Place potato on table.
anns.task_desc: Robot should find, slice, brown potato. Once cooked,  place potato on table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Take the knife from the counter.
Cut the potato into slices.
Stand in front of the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Stand in front of the counter.
Take a slice of potato.
Walk to the right and stop in front of the stove.
Put the potato slice into the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the potato slice from the microwave.
Turn around, walk straight and to the right towards the white trash bag. Turn right and face the white table.
Put the slice of potato on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put the microwaved slice of potato on the white table.
